==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*βλασφημέω / blasphēmeō / blas-fay-meh'-o
*From G989; to vilify; specifically to speak impiously: 

===Verb===
'''βλασφημέω'''

# (speak) [[blaspheme]] (-er, -mously, -my), [[defame]], rail on, [[revile]], speak evil.

